<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Moves capable of freezing have a very low chance of doing so. Moreover, Magma Armor suffers from terrible distribution: only three Pokemon get it, only two of which are fully evolved. <a href="/bw/pokemon/magcargo">Magcargo</a> is useless either way no thanks to its awful Speed, and <a href="/bw/pokemon/camerupt">Camerupt</a> has a better option in <a href="/bw/abilities/solid_rock">Solid Rock</a>. Keep away from this.</p>